ter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2><strong>帕拉摩尔的歌单是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“你第一”<br /> 2.“新闻”<br /> 3.“这就是你得到的”<br /> 4.“扮演上帝”<br /> 5.“夹在中间”<br /> 6.《玫瑰色男孩》<br /> 7.“时间不多了”<br /> 8.“解码”<br /> 9.“大男人，小尊严”<br /> 10.“骗子”<br /> 11.《Crystal Clear》（海莉·威廉姆斯歌曲）<br /> 12.《Hard Times》（带有 Blondie 的《Heart of Glass》片段）<br /> 13.《早就告诉过你了》<br /> 14.“图8”<br /> 15.“唯一的例外”<br /> 16.“渴望”<br /> 17.《宝贝》（HalfNoise 封面）<br /> 18.《苦难事业》<br /> 19.“这不是很有趣吗”<br /> 20.《我想要的一切》（与比莉·艾利什合作）<br /> 21.《依然喜欢你》</strong><br /> <strong>22.“这就是为什么”（与 MUNA 合作）</strong></p><p>本月早些时候，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-paramore-hayley-williams-cover-beyonce-i-miss-you-live-footage-setlist-3467916">威廉姆斯翻唱了碧昂斯的《我想你》之后，帕拉莫尔乐队再次成为头条新闻。</a>这一刻发生在他们在休斯敦的演出期间——“单身女士”歌手出生在同一座城市。 </p><figure id="attachment_3431066" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3431066" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3431066" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_paramore_hayleywilliams_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="帕拉摩尔乐队的海莉·威廉姆斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_paramore_hayleywilliams_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_paramore_hayleywilliams_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_paramore_hayleywilliams_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_paramore_hayleywilliams_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_paramore_hayleywilliams_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_paramore_hayleywilliams_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3431066" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 2 月 9 日，Paramore 乐队的 Hayley Williams 在百威淡啤超级碗音乐节第一晚在亚利桑那州凤凰城足迹中心的舞台上表演（图片来源：Aaron J. Thornton/WireImage）</figcaption></figure><p>在同一场演出中，他们还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-paramore-sing-misery-business-with-nine-year-old-fan-3468574">邀请了一位九岁的粉丝和他们一起</a>表演了《苦难事业》，俘获了粉丝们的心。</p><p>在帕拉莫尔的其他新闻中，最近宣布乐队将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-adds-uk-and-eu-eras-tour-dates-with-paramore-ruling-her-out-of-glastonbury-3465195">新宣布的英国和欧洲巡演日期</a>期间为她提供支持。</p><p>在威廉姆斯和斯威夫特合作歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-taylor-swifts-collaborations-with-hayley-williams-and-fall-out-boy-3466259">“城堡崩溃”</a>之后，他们与这位“反英雄”歌手一起巡演的消息传出。这首歌曲收录在她本月早些时候发行的重新录制的专辑“Speak Now（泰勒版）”中。</p><p>流行朋克乐队和 MUNA 都支持泰勒·斯威夫特的“Eras”巡演，但从未在同一日期演出。然而，他们确实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-kendrick-lamar-odesza-zeds-dead-and-more-announced-for-bonnaroo-2023-3378504">出现在博纳罗音乐节的同一阵容中</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-hayley-williams-join-billie-eilish-at-coachella-2022-to-cover-paramores-misery-business-3210917">去年，艾利什还与帕拉莫尔一起出现在科切拉音乐节的舞台上</a>，两人都表演了《Misery Business》。这是乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-axe-controversial-track-misery-business-live-shows-2377010">在 2018 年最初将这首热门歌曲从演出中退役</a>后首次表演。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-muna-join-paramore-los-angeles-footage-setlist-3471066">观看 Billie Eilish 和 MUNA 与 Paramore 一起在洛杉矶登台表演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
动视暴雪在裁员后让《守望先锋》联赛陷入困境https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/activision-blizzard-leaves-overwatch-league-in-the-lurch-after-layoffs-3471055?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=activision-blizzard-leaves-overwatch-league-in-the-lurch-after-layoffsImogen Donovan Thu, 20 Jul 2023 11:53:16 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsesportsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3471055 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>此次裁员“令所有人震惊”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首先报道了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/activision-blizzard-leaves-overwatch-league-in-the-lurch-after-layoffs-3471055">裁员消息，动视暴雪让《守望先锋》联赛陷入困境</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/overwatch"><em>《守望先锋</em></a>联赛》的未来掌握在战队老板手中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision-blizzard">动视暴雪</a>在本财年第二季度对其电子竞技部门进行了重大调整。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：弗兰基<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-frankie-ward-3469756">·沃德 (Frankie Ward) 是电子竞技偶像</a></strong></li></ul><p>动视暴雪在<a href="https://investor.activision.com/news-releases/news-release-details/activision-blizzard-announces-second-quarter-2023-financial">最新的收益报告</a>中解释说，将在本赛季结束时向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/overwatch-2-to-hold-an-lgbtq-tournament-this-month-3320777"><em>《守望先锋</em>联赛》</a>队伍提供“更新后的运营协议”。</p><p>声明中写道：“如果球队不投票同意按照更新后的运营协议继续进行，则将向每个参与球队实体支付 600 万美元（465 万英镑）的终止费（总费用约为 1.14 亿美元（8840 万英镑）”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3471070" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3471070" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3471070" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/overwatch-2-esports-layoffs-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3471070" class="wp-caption-text"> 《守望先锋》球队旧金山震动队庆祝 2019 年总决赛胜利 图片来源：Jen Smith 来自 Wikimedia Commons</figcaption></figure><p>它还解雇了大约 50 名电子竞技员工，根据<em><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/19/23799550/activision-blizzard-esports-layoffs-overwatch-league-owl">The Verge</a></em>的报道，这些改变<em>《守望先锋</em>联赛》的举措非常有意义。受疫情影响，动视暴雪欠《<em>守望先锋》</em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/call-of-duty">《使命召唤》</a></em>职业联赛约 4 亿美元的特许经营费。</p><p>此外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/blizzard-entertainment">暴雪娱乐</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netease">网易</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/netease-ends-contract-with-activision-blizzard-making-several-titles-unavailable-in-china-3382221">在中国支持其游戏的</a>合作关系解散，导致<em>《守望先锋》</em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hearthstone"><em>《炉石传说》</em></a>等游戏下线。成都猎人队随后退出了《<em>守望先锋</em>联赛》，由于其巨大的人气，在名单上留下了一个很大的空缺。</p><p> <em>《守望先锋</em>联赛》专员肖恩·米勒表示，无论队伍是否支持《<em>守望先锋</em>联赛》，2024 年《守望先锋联赛》都将出现“全球复兴”。 “我们正在尽一切努力让玩家体验和粉丝体验成为人们想要回归、想要成为其中的一部分、并为开启而兴奋的体验，”他解释道。</p><p>然而，一位受到最近裁员影响的匿名前雇员表示，这“让每个人都感到彻底震惊”。他们辩解道：“当你的公司利润创纪录，而你的股价因即将到来的收购而触底时，我真的无法理解裁员有什么好处。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，配音演员维多利亚·阿特金表达了她对非官方游戏模组<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/assassins-creed-voice-actor-describes-ai-as-an-invisible-enemy-3471042">人工生成声音激增的</a>担忧。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>首先报道了<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/activision-blizzard-leaves-overwatch-league-in-the-lurch-after-layoffs-3471055">裁员消息，动视暴雪让《守望先锋》联赛陷入困境</a>。</p> ;
 Netflix 取消了美国和英国最便宜的无广告套餐https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-axes-cheapest-ad-free-plan-us-uk-3471064?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=netflix-axes-cheapest-ad-free-plan-us-ukAdam Starkey Thu, 20 Jul 2023 11:45:35 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3471064 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Netflix 徽标" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>新会员或回归会员不再适用 £6.99/$9.99 计划</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-axes-cheapest-ad-free-plan-us-uk-3471064">Netflix 取消了美国和英国最便宜的无广告套餐</a>后，首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Netflix 徽标" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Netflix-logo-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>放弃了美国和英国最便宜的无广告套餐。</p><p>上个月在加拿大首次淘汰后，基本的无广告套餐（在英国售价为 6.99 英镑，在美国售价为 9.99 美元）在这两个国家已不再向新会员和重新加入会员提供。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/why-are-actors-striking-in-hollywood-3468340">好莱坞演员为何罢工？</a></strong></li></ul><p>不过，只要您不取消或更改计划，当前订阅该计划的用户就可以保留订阅。</p><p>在<a href="https://s22.q4cdn.com/959853165/files/doc_financials/2023/q2/FINAL-Q2-23-Shareholder-Letter.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">周三（7 月 19 日）发布的</a>公司财报电话报告中，Netflix 写道：“第一季度，我们在一些渗透率较低的市场降低了价格，第二季度，我们逐步取消了针对加拿大新会员和重新加入会员的基本无广告计划（基本无广告计划的现有会员不受影响）。我们现在在美国和英国也在做同样的事情。</p><p> “我们相信，鉴于我们产品目录的广度和质量，我们在这些国家的入门价格（美国 6.99 美元、英国 4.99 英镑、加拿大 5.99 美元）为消费者提供了巨大的价值。” </p><figure id="attachment_3296938" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3296938" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3296938" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/StrangerThings_StrangerThings4_6_00_45_39_21-1.jpg" alt="陌生的事物" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/StrangerThings_StrangerThings4_6_00_45_39_21-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/StrangerThings_StrangerThings4_6_00_45_39_21-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/StrangerThings_StrangerThings4_6_00_45_39_21-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/StrangerThings_StrangerThings4_6_00_45_39_21-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/StrangerThings_StrangerThings4_6_00_45_39_21-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/StrangerThings_StrangerThings4_6_00_45_39_21-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3296938" class="wp-caption-text">米莉·鲍比·布朗在《怪奇物语》中饰演十一号 图片来源：Netflix 提供</figcaption></figure><p>随着基本的无广告计划的取消，Netflix 现在提供三个订阅级别：每月 4.99 英镑/6.99 美元的广告支持计划、10.99 英镑/15.49 英镑的无广告标准计划以及每月 15.99 英镑/19.99 美元的高级套餐（支持提高视频质量）。</p><p>在同一份报告中，Netflix 表示，自 3 月份以来，该流媒体服务<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-password-sharing-restrictions-explained-3391288">打击家庭之间的密码共享行为</a>，全球订阅用户数量增加了 590 万。这一变化意味着 Netflix 用户必须支付额外费用才能将更多会员添加到他们的帐户中。</p><p> Netflix 还预计内容支出将下降，部分原因是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/famous-actors-striking-hollywood-picket-lines-sag-aftra-3469811">美国演员工会 (SAG-AFTRA) 和美国编剧工会 (WGA) 正在进行罢工</a>。该公司在致股东的信中写道：“我们现在预计 2023 年 FCF（自由现金流）至少为 50 亿美元，高于我们之前估计的至少 35 亿美元。”</p><p> “由于生产开始时间以及 WGA 和 SAG-AFTRA 正在进行的罢工，我们更新的预期反映了 2023 年现金内容支出低于我们最初的预期。”</p><p> Netflix 的许多节目的制作都受到 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/heres-every-tv-show-film-affected-by-writers-strike-3442270">了持续罢工的影响</a>，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/production-on-stranger-things-final-season-paused-until-writers-strike-deal-reached-3440429"><em>《怪奇物语》</em>第五季和最后一季</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-axes-cheapest-ad-free-plan-us-uk-3471064">Netflix 取消了美国和英国最便宜的无广告套餐</a>后，首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《刺客信条》配音演员将人工智能描述为“看不见的敌人” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/assassins-creed-voice-actor-describes-ai-as-an-invisible-enemy-3471042?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=assassins-creed-voice-actor-describes-ai-as-an-invisible-enemyImogen Donovan Thu, 20 Jul 2023 11:18:17 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsModsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3471042 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这太可怕了”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/assassins-creed-voice-actor-describes-ai-as-an-invisible-enemy-3471042">《刺客信条》配音演员将人工智能描述为“看不见的敌人”，该配音</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/assassins-creed-voice-actor-decries-ai-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在《刺客<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/assassins-creed-syndicate"><em>信条：枭雄》中扮演伊维·弗莱的</em></a>配音演员维多利亚·阿特金批评使用人工智能软件为模组模拟声音，称其为“看不见的敌人”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：弗兰基<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-frankie-ward-3469756">·沃德 (Frankie Ward) 是电子竞技偶像</a></strong></li></ul><p>“真的，我有点震惊，它在未经我同意的情况下就被使用了，它就在那里，”她在接受<em><a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/assassins-creed-voice-actor-calls-ai-generated-mods-the-invisible-enemy-were-fighting-right-now">IGN</a></em>采访时说道，因为她意识到自己的声音在未经她许可的情况<a href="https://twitter.com/VictoriaAtkin/status/1680070771891388417?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1680070771891388417%7Ctwgr%5Eef99ff43cb2501546205430779ff844955fd4308%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ign.com%2Farticles%2Fassassins-creed-voice-actor-calls-ai-generated-mods-the-invisible-enemy-were-fighting-right-now">下出现在了模组中</a>。</p><p> “想到我的生活可能会被剥夺，因为有人可以复制它并修改它，让我说他们想让我说的任何话，这是非常可怕的......这是一种无处不在的威胁。这有点像我们现在正在对抗的这个看不见的敌人，”阿特金继续说道。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">更新一下……人工智能刚刚偷走了我这个角色的声音。 <a href="https://twitter.com/sagaftra?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@sagaftra</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/WGAEast?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@WGAEast</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/WGAWest?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@WGAWest</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Unionstrong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Unionstrong</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/videogames?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#videogames</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/performancecapture?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#performancecapture</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/eviefrye?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#eviefrye</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/AssassinsCreed?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#AssassinsCreed</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/assassinscreed?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@assassinscreed</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/Ubisoft?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Ubisoft</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/latimes?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@latimes</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/Variety?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Variety</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/DEADLINE?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@DEADLINE</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/IGN?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@IGN</a> <a href="https://t.co/IUGta4Pssh">https://t.co/IUGta4Pssh</a></p><p> — 维多利亚·阿特金 (@VictoriaAtkin) <a href="https://twitter.com/VictoriaAtkin/status/1680070771891388417?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 15 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>本月早些时候，一名<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-v-skyrim"><em>《天际》</em></a>粉丝曝光了在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/video-game-voice-actors-denounce-nsfw-mods-ai-deepfakes-voices-3466276">色情模组</a>中使用人工智能复制阿普丽尔·斯图尔特、保罗·加努斯、乔恩·库里等演员的声音的情况。</p><p>相关人员对此表示难以置信，但 Nexus Mods 对人工智能生成内容的立场是灵活的。只有当“受影响的创作者/权利持有者”提出“可信的投诉”时，模组网站才会考虑下架该模组。</p><p>阿特金补充说，一想到她的声音可能会如何通过这些工具被使用，她深感担忧，因为人工智能太新了，无法包含在她签署的大量合同中。</p><p> “我已经完成了太多的游戏，我已经记不清了，而且有太多我的声音，我永远无法追踪……有些游戏的制作人员甚至没有出现在我的 IMDb 上，”她说。 “他们不经我同意就拿它做什么，这有点危险。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/insomniac-games">Insomniac Games</a>分享了即将推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a>独占<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/marvels-spider-man-2"><em>《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》</em></a>中有关毒液的一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/marvels-spider-man-2-director-was-so-scared-to-get-venom-wrong-3470948">新信息</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/assassins-creed-voice-actor-describes-ai-as-an-invisible-enemy-3471042">《刺客信条》配音演员将人工智能描述为“看不见的敌人”，该配音</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
酷玩乐队宣布 2024 年欧洲体育场巡演日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-2024-european-stadium-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3471050?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=coldplay-announce-2024-european-stadium-tour-dates-buy-ticketsLiberty Dunworth Thu, 20 Jul 2023 11:12:43 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3471050 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="酷玩乐队 2023 年现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这些日期包括他们在希腊、罗马尼亚和芬兰的首次演出</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-2024-european-stadium-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3471050">酷玩乐队宣布 2024 年欧洲体育场巡演日期的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="酷玩乐队 2023 年现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Coldplay@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay)</a>宣布了一系列欧洲体育场巡演日期，定于 2024 年夏季举行。请在下面查找门票信息和日期列表。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/coldplay-live-in-london-wembley-stadium-music-of-the-spheres-natalie-umbruglia-3292045">酷玩乐队伦敦演唱会：一场梦幻般、令人感觉良好的盛宴，兑现了大胆的承诺</a></strong></li></ul><p>新一轮的巡演日期是在乐队于 5 月开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-add-new-2023-uk-european-gigs-to-music-of-the-spheres-world-tour-3294809">的 2023 年体育场演出</a>之后到来的。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">克里斯·马丁</a>和他的同事们都看过这个节目。登上巴塞罗那、曼彻斯特、卡迪夫、米兰等地的舞台。</p><p>现在，根据粉丝在当前系列现场表演中的反应，乐队宣布了 2024 年 6 月、7 月和 8 月的第三轮欧洲演出。</p><p>作为他们破纪录的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/coldplay-music-of-the-spheres-review-3070711">“Music Of The Spheres”</a>世界巡演的一部分，新宣布的演出将在希腊、罗马尼亚和芬兰首次进行现场表演，并自 2008 年以来首次访问布达佩斯。</p><p> Kicking off with a show in Athens on June 8, Coldplay are also set to play their first gig in Rome in over 20 years, with the last concert in the city being held back in 2003. Although no UK dates are included this time around, the four-piece will end their upcoming 2024 dates with two back-to-back performances in Dublin at the end of August. </p><figure id="attachment_3449741" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3449741" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3449741" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Coldplay-performing.jpg" alt="Chris Martin of Coldplay performs on stage at Estadi Olimpic on May 24, 2023 in Barcelona, Spain. Credit: Jordi Vidal/ Getty" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Coldplay-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Coldplay-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Coldplay-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Coldplay-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Coldplay-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Coldplay-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3449741" class="wp-caption-text"> Chris Martin of Coldplay performs on stage at Estadi Olimpic on May 24, 2023 in Barcelona, Spain. Credit: Jordi Vidal/ Getty</figcaption></figure><p> Pre-sale tickets go live next Tuesday (July 15), at 9am local time in Athens, Bucharest, Budapest, Lyon, Rome and Helsinki, and at 10am local time in Dusseldorf, Munich, Vienna and Dublin. Fans can register for <a href="https://www.coldplay.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">access here</a> .</p><p> Additionally, general on-sale will commence next Friday (July 28) and will go live at 10am local time for all cities, and a limited number of affordable &#39;Infinity Tickets&#39; will also be on offer. Tickets will be <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcoldplay-tickets%2Fartist%2F806431" target="_blank" rel="noopener">available here</a> , and you can find a full list of 2024 tour dates below.</p><h2> <strong>Coldplay&#39;s 2024 European tour dates are:</strong></h2><p> <strong>JUNE</strong><br /> <strong>8 — Olympic Stadium, Athens</strong><br /> <strong>12 — Arena Națională, Bucharest</strong><br /> <strong>16 — Puskás Aréna, Budapest</strong><br /> <strong>22 —Groupama Stadium, Lyon</strong><br /> <strong>23 — Groupama Stadium, Lyon</strong></p><p><strong>七月</strong><br /><strong>12 — Stadio Olimpico, Rome</strong><br /> <strong>13 —Stadio Olimpico, Rome</strong><br /> <strong>20 — Merkur Spiel-Arena, Düsseldorf</strong><br /> <strong>21 —Merkur Spiel-Arena, Düsseldorf</strong><br /> <strong>28 — Olympiastadion, Helsinki</strong></p><p><strong>八月</strong><br /><strong>15 — Olympiastadion, Munich</strong><br /> <strong>17 — Olympiastadion, Munich</strong><br /> <strong>21 — Ernst-Happel-Stadion, Vienna</strong><br /> <strong>22 — Ernst-Happel-Stadion, Vienna</strong><br /> <strong>29 — Croke Park, Dublin</strong><br /> <strong>30 — Croke Park, Dublin</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3387655" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3387655" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3387655" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/2023_coldplay_getty_2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="酷玩乐队" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/2023_coldplay_getty_2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/2023_coldplay_getty_2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/2023_coldplay_getty_2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/2023_coldplay_getty_2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/2023_coldplay_getty_2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/2023_coldplay_getty_2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3387655" class="wp-caption-text"> Chris Martin of Coldplay performs during the first of ten shows as part of &#39;Music Of The Spheres World Tour&#39; at Estadio Mas Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti on October 25, 2022 in Buenos Aires CREDIT: Santiago Bluguermann/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> In other Coldplay news, it was reported by Massachusetts Institute of Technology that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplays-eco-friendly-tour-has-reduced-their-carbon-emissions-by-nearly-half-3451303">Coldplay&#39;s current tour has so far produced 47% less carbon emissions than their previous stadium tour in 2016/17</a> . The band have also taken extra precautions to be green by planting 5 million trees around the world – one for each concertgoer so far.</p><p> They also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-us-music-of-the-spheres-tour-dates-3385301">announced a series of US tour dates</a> earlier this year, as well as <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/coldplay-music-of-the-spheres-asia-australia-tour-dates-tickets-3440975">a run of shows in Australia and Asia</a> .</p><p> In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/coldplay-live-in-london-wembley-stadium-music-of-the-spheres-natalie-umbruglia-3292045">a five-star review of their London gig</a> last year, <em>NME</em> praised Martin and co. for their ability to deliver a captivating set, alongside “a focus on sustainability and inclusivity”. “The songs performed here see the band strip things back, injecting the larger-than-life show with a moment of closeness. There&#39;s a poignant version of &#39;Parachute&#39; track &#39;Sparks&#39;, which is followed by special guests joining the band on stage,” it read.</p><p> “It&#39;s a joyful spectacle; a masterclass in how a massive pop show can be done. The band seem genuinely thrilled at the reaction, too.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-2024-european-stadium-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3471050">Coldplay announce 2024 European stadium tour dates</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
